1. Ulo weji kulingisanga ngachilihi tanga kupwa yakuwahilila? Mujimbu wamwaza wafuma kuli Yehova, Kalunga wakuwahilila, uze asaka tanga hitanga yipwenga yakuwahilila. (WaChimoteu 1, 1:11) Ikiye ahakileko ulo. Kulimbata kweseka najishimbi cheji kulingisanga tanga yipwenga yakuwahilila mwomwo yapwa hichihela chamwaza chakulelelamo vana. Uno Kalunga amona ngachilihi ulo? Kalunga asaka valunga napwevo valimbata vatwamenga hamwe myaka yosena. Vaka-Kulishitu vatela kuvumbika jishimbi jamulifuchi lyavo
..........
mukwavo. (Wavaka-Kolinde 1, 13:4, 5) Mazu aKalunga kawasolola nge kulihandununa chikiko cheji kukumisanga ukalu muuloko.—Tangenu Wavaka-Kolinde 1, 7:10-13. 4. Enu vana, uno Kalunga asaka vyuma muka kuli enu? Yehova asaka mupwenga vakuwahilila. Amilweza mwakutwamina kanawa numba mulivwise kuwaha ukweze wenu. Asaka munganyale kumangana nachinyingi chavisemi jenu. (Wavaka-Kolose 3:20) Yehova asaka nawa mulivwise kuwaha chize chatwama hakuzachila Tengi naMwanenyi.—Tangenu Muka-kwambulula 11:9–12:1;
